			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>You rise a few inches above the ground and glide over minor hindrances.</i></p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Daily âœ¦ Arcane</b></p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Minor Action</b><b> &#8226; </b>Personal</p><p><b>Effect:</b> You hover 6 inches above the ground until the end of the encounter or until you fall. You ignore movement penalties and restrictions due to terrain, do not set off pressure-sensitive traps, and cannot be detected with tremorsense. You also gain a bonus to Stealth checks equal to your Wisdom modifier. You can float over only a solid surface or a liquid surface directly beneath you. For example, you cannot use this power to cross a chasm or a pit; if you try to do so, you fall normally. </p><p>Published in Arcane Power, page(s) 103. </p>",
